item.title: My Boyfriend Does My Makeup
item.description:
My Boyfriend Does My Makeup
Hey everyone! This video has been highly requested for quite some time now. It took mega convincing to get Tim to agree to this video. It took even longer waiting for him to be free (He was busy playing Diablo 3) to do this tag. Tim and I have been together for 9 years now. He's not only my Bubba but my bestest friend in the World ^_^. He was very nervous about doing my makeup but eventually really got into it during the video. I can tell he was having fun (even though he doesn't admit it haha) I'm proud of him. We had a good banter for sure. The makeover he gave me looks better than any of the 'makeovers' I give him on my Bubbiosity channel anyways! I'm sure you'll see Tim in more of my videos in the future. For now, you can check out my Vlog Channel to see more of him ^_^ http://www.youtube.com/bubzvlogz Ps. I compressed the video from 40 minutes to 9 minutes because he spent a lot of time deciding which products to use and "looking for instructions". Didn't want the video to be too long for you guys. Pps. Chubbi & Domo got haircuts! Cute huh? You can check out their recent doggy blog post at: http://www.bubzbeauty.com/chubbi/320-chubbi-a-domo-got-haircuts.html Ppps. Check out my latest post "Top 5 Drugstore Foundations" at: http://www.bubzbeauty.com/reviews/318-top-drugstore-foundations.html Pppps. Yes, my accent has gotten stronger since coming back from Northern Ireland ^_^ It's especially strong when Tim is around too tehee. Until next time! Take care everyone!
